{"word":"πορνεύω","slug":"πορνεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πορνεύω</el></b> [<el>πέρνημι</el> ‘sell’ via <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πόρνη\">πόρνη</a></el>] <b>fornicate <a href='B:480 10:19'>Mk 10:19</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:530 6:18'>1 Cor 6:18</a>; <a href='B:530 10:8'>10:8</a>;</b> unless used in a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ metaph.\">metaph.</a> sense <b><a href='B:730 2:14'>Rv 2:14</a>, <a href='B:730 2:20'>20</a></b> belong here<b>.</b> By <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a>, in imagistic sense: of idolatrous conduct of the apocalyptic whore’s activity <b><a href='B:730 17:2'>Rv 17:2</a>; <a href='B:730 18:3'>18:3</a>, <a href='B:730 18:9'>9</a>;</b> for<b> <a href='B:730 2:14'>2:14</a>, <a href='B:730 2:20'>20</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> above. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πορνεία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πόρνη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}